---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="FASTag Recharge Online | TrueCred Loan Expert">

<!-- Page Hero -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <a href="/pages/recharge-bills">Recharge &amp; Bills</a>
        <span class="sep"><i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i></span>
        <span>FASTag Recharge</span>
      </div>
      <h1>FASTag Recharge Online</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Recharge your FASTag instantly for seamless toll payments across all national and state highways. All bank FASTags supported — NHAI linked, 100% secure.</p>
      <div class="hero-highlights">
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-road"></i> Banks: All Major
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> Balance Update: Instant
        </div>
        <div class="highlight-item">
          <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i> NHAI Linked
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Page Content -->
  <section class="page-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <div class="content-main">
          <h2>Keep Your FASTag Topped Up, Travel Non-Stop</h2>
          <p>Never get stuck at a toll plaza again. TrueCred Loan Expert lets you recharge your FASTag online in seconds, no matter which bank issued it. Our platform is linked directly to the NHAI (National Highways Authority of India) system, ensuring your balance is updated instantly and reflected at toll plazas across the country.</p>
          <p>Whether you drive daily for work or take occasional highway trips, keeping your FASTag balance healthy is essential. With TrueCred, you can also set up low-balance alerts and auto-recharge so you never run out of toll balance mid-journey.</p>

          <!-- Supported Banks Table -->
          <h3>Supported FASTag Issuing Banks</h3>
          <div class="table-responsive" style="overflow-x:auto; margin: 24px 0 40px;">
            <table style="width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; min-width:600px;">
              <thead>
                <tr style="background: var(--primary); color: #fff;">
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:left;">Bank</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Min Recharge</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Max Recharge</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Instant Update</th>
                  <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">Auto-Recharge</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">SBI</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹100</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹1,00,000</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">HDFC Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹100</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹1,00,000</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">ICICI Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹100</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹1,00,000</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb; background: #f9fafb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Axis Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹100</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹1,00,000</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                </tr>
                <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Paytm Payments Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹100</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹1,00,000</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; font-weight:600;">Kotak Mahindra Bank</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹100</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center;">₹1,00,000</td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                  <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align:center; color: green;"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
          <p style="color:#6b7280; font-size: 0.9rem;">* All NHAI-approved FASTag issuing banks are supported. The table shows select popular banks.</p>

          <!-- Benefits -->
          <h2>Why Recharge FASTag on TrueCred?</h2>
          <ul class="feature-list">
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>All Banks Supported:</strong> Recharge FASTags issued by SBI, HDFC, ICICI, Axis, Paytm, Kotak, and 30+ other banks</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Instant Balance Update:</strong> Your FASTag balance is updated in real-time via NHAI's NETC system</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Low Balance Alerts:</strong> Get SMS/email alerts when your FASTag balance drops below a threshold you set</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Auto-Recharge:</strong> Set up auto top-up via UPI mandate so your FASTag never runs dry on the highway</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Transaction History:</strong> View all toll deductions and recharge history in one place for expense tracking</li>
            <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Secure &amp; NHAI Linked:</strong> Direct integration with NHAI's National Electronic Toll Collection system</li>
          </ul>

          <!-- How It Works -->
          <h2>How to Recharge Your FASTag</h2>
          <p>Top up your FASTag in 4 easy steps.</p>
          <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">1</div>
              <h4>Select Issuing Bank</h4>
              <p>Choose the bank that issued your FASTag from the dropdown list.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">2</div>
              <h4>Enter Vehicle Number</h4>
              <p>Enter your vehicle registration number or FASTag ID linked to your tag.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">3</div>
              <h4>Enter Amount &amp; Pay</h4>
              <p>Enter the recharge amount and pay via UPI, net banking, or debit/credit card.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
              <div class="step-num">4</div>
              <h4>Balance Updated</h4>
              <p>Your FASTag balance is updated instantly. Confirmation sent via SMS and email.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Page CTA -->
          <div class="page-cta">
            <div>
              <h3>Need a Car Loan or Insurance?</h3>
              <p>Compare car loans from top lenders or explore comprehensive vehicle insurance plans.</p>
            </div>
            <a href="/pages/car-loan" class="btn btn-outline">Check Car Loans <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <div class="content-sidebar">
          <!-- FASTag Recharge Form -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-road" style="color: var(--primary); margin-right: 6px;"></i> FASTag Recharge</h3>
            <form class="sidebar-form" onsubmit="return false;">
              <div class="form-group">
                <select class="form-input">
                  <option value="">Select Issuing Bank</option>
                  <option value="sbi">SBI</option>
                  <option value="hdfc">HDFC Bank</option>
                  <option value="icici">ICICI Bank</option>
                  <option value="axis">Axis Bank</option>
                  <option value="paytm">Paytm Payments Bank</option>
                  <option value="kotak">Kotak Mahindra Bank</option>
                  <option value="bob">Bank of Baroda</option>
                  <option value="other">Other Bank</option>
                </select>
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="Vehicle Registration Number">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="text" class="form-input" placeholder="FASTag ID (Optional)">
              </div>
              <div class="form-group">
                <input type="number" class="form-input" placeholder="Recharge Amount (₹)">
              </div>
              <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" style="width:100%;justify-content:center;">
                Recharge FASTag <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>

          <!-- Quick Links -->
          <div class="sidebar-card">
            <h3>Other Services</h3>
            <div class="sidebar-links">
              <a href="/pages/mobile-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Mobile Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/electricity-bill"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Electricity Bill Payment</a>
              <a href="/pages/dth-recharge"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> DTH Recharge</a>
              <a href="/pages/lpg-gas-booking"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> LPG Gas Booking</a>
              <a href="/pages/loan-emi-payment"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Loan EMI Payment</a>
              <a href="/pages/car-loan"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Car Loan</a>
              <a href="/pages/insurance"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> Vehicle Insurance</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Section -->
  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <span class="section-tag">FAQs</span>
        <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
        <p>Common questions about FASTag recharge on TrueCred.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-list">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Which bank FASTags can I recharge on TrueCred?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              TrueCred supports FASTag recharges for all NHAI-approved issuing banks including SBI, HDFC Bank, ICICI Bank, Axis Bank, Paytm Payments Bank, Kotak Mahindra Bank, Bank of Baroda, Punjab National Bank, IndusInd Bank, and 25+ other banks. If your FASTag is issued by an NHAI-approved bank, you can recharge it here.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            How quickly will my FASTag balance be updated?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              FASTag recharges are processed instantly through the NHAI NETC (National Electronic Toll Collection) system. Your balance is typically updated within 30 seconds to 2 minutes of successful payment. The updated balance will be reflected at toll plazas across all national and state highways.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            What is the minimum and maximum FASTag recharge amount?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              The minimum recharge amount for FASTag is ₹100 and the maximum is ₹1,00,000 per transaction. The maximum wallet balance allowed on a FASTag is also ₹1,00,000 as per NHAI guidelines. We recommend keeping a minimum balance of ₹500 for uninterrupted highway travel.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Can I set up auto-recharge for my FASTag?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Yes, TrueCred offers auto-recharge for FASTag via UPI mandate. You can set a minimum balance threshold (e.g., ₹200) and a top-up amount (e.g., ₹500). When your FASTag balance drops below the threshold, it will automatically be recharged. You'll receive a notification before each auto-debit.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question">
            Where can I find my FASTag ID or vehicle registration number?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <div class="faq-answer-inner">
              Your FASTag ID is printed on the FASTag sticker affixed to your vehicle's windshield. You can also find it in the confirmation SMS/email you received when the FASTag was issued. Alternatively, simply use your vehicle registration number (e.g., MH12AB1234) to look up your FASTag on TrueCred.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->

</BaseLayout>
